  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacodynamic Profile of Oral 2101 in Secondary Raynaud's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo-controlled, Cross-over Pilot Study to Examine the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Profile of Repeat Oral Doses of SLx-2101 Once Daily for up to 14 Days in Subjects With Secondary Raynaud's Disease.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
